      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a total gem? I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s in showroom condition! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014not a single blemish inside or out. It drives like a dream and still has that new-car smell. You really have to see it to believe how pristine it is. Come take it for a spin, you won't be disappointed!",
