    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-grade condition. This specimen features the iconic S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, delivering linear power through six individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double-VANOS system. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. This vehicle has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity. The suspension remains taut with factory-spec bushings and dampers, while the exterior retains its original deep-gloss finish with zero paint correction required. An immaculate interior with supple Nappa leather and functional electronics makes this a turnkey example for the discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
